                    <p>These cookies collect anonymized data that is not related to an identified or identifiable natural person.</p>
                    <p>These cookies are valid for varying periods; some are deleted once you close your browser, while others have an indefinite validity period.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
